  "title": "Design & Content Senior Executive #ESY",
  "description": "<p>•\tManage social media platforms, including content planning, posting schedules, website and Intranet updates and website revamp.</p><p>•\tDevelop engaging, audience-focused content, including student stories, research highlights, event promotions, and scholarship features.</p><p>•\tDesign and produce marketing materials in a variety of formats, including print, video, and digital platforms.</p><p>•\tSupport outreach initiatives and events management, including postgraduate events, career fairs, and information sessions.</p><p>•\tProvide administrative support on partnership matters and related activities.</p><p><br /></p><p>Interested candidates, please email your resume to annasee@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p></p><p>Anna See Sing Yee</p><p>CEI Reg R25157535</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 99C4599</p><p></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted</p><p><br /></p>",
